item.title: Next Step - Mia Nix, Alberto Blanco
item.description: Mia and Alberto have nothing in common... almost nothing. In their case, friction makes sparks, and sparks make for more friction.

item.title: Ride Or Die - Gianna Dior, April Olsen, Maximo Garcia
item.description: When she returns from her European vacation, Gianna brings a souvenir back for her good friend April. Here's hoping April likes conquistadors.

item.title: Jia's Daydream - Jia Lissa, Alberto Blanco
item.description: An awkward reception at an ultra-posh party forces Jia to escape into fantasy. Once she's down the rabbit hole, this redhead's revery reveals how fair maidens behaved behind closed doors in the long gone days of yore.

item.title: Fortunate Buns - Britt Blair, Maximo Garcia
item.description: Britt doesn't believe in the law of attraction, but people will believe what they want to hear. When a tarot reader tells Britt she's going to meet a total fuck machine, she digs deep inside and manifests one into being.

item.title: Morning Surprise - Honour May, Vince Karter
item.description: They say you always remember your first, but Honour's initial attempt at anal didn't break any boundaries or blow any minds. She wants it to work... and it won't be a chore if she can have fun working it in.

item.title: Office Grind - Liv Revamped, Mick Blue
item.description: Liv is determined to make her work as a personal assistant exciting: if that means violating the dress code and copping an attitude, so be it. She'll pour the coffee every day, so long as someone reminds her who's boss.

item.title: Good Vibes - Violet Myers, Alex Jones, Oliver Flynn
item.description: Violet was so excited for this barbeque, until the weather rained all over her vibes. But if Violet can't grab a hot dog, maybe she can still get a sandwich.

item.title: Playing Nice - Asia Vargas, Alberto Blanco
item.description: Asia is vacationing with friends at a villa. Asia likes Alberto, whose girlfriend is awful. She waits in the wings for Alberto to break up, then pounces.

item.title: In Bloom - Alex H Banks, Mick Blue
item.description: Alex caught the bouquet, but she's not the marrying kind. She's more the "anal in the morning" kind your mother doesn't want to know about.

item.title: Spicing It Up - Jane Wilde, Oliver Flynn
item.description: Jane and her boyfriend are away on vacation, and what's the point of taking a trip if you don't try new things? Jane has a plan, and if the end result isn't a surprise for her, at least she can make it special for him.
